item.description:
1st floor has a dual piano bar and lounge, upstairs is a nightclub

 

Dress Code: dress to impress. No baggy jeans, no hats, no boots or logos.

jeans and sneakers ok, nice button down shirts, dress shirts/club shirts

Cover is $10. We will meet at the piano bar at 10:30, then head upstairs at some point.

 

Text, call or email with any questions. When you arrive, send me a text message and I can direct you to where we are. :-) Can't wait to meet and see everyone there
